ing in the studies of the broad-line regions. The\nlack of evolution for the gas metallicity of the narrow-line regions implies\nthat the major epoch of star formation in the host galaxies of these active\ngalactic nuclei is at z > 4.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Aug 2005 17:20:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
