ops a pronounced peak. The asymptotic behavior of the energy peak location\nis used to locate the critical temperature, which is also found to be universal\nand in accordance with the mean-field prediction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2005 13:07:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
